IbrarYunus
BSCS-2B

___

A Java based File Crawler and Indexer.
* 1st Pass: Indexes Files and saves their size, name and sbolute path in a list
* Gives the user to searhc for files based on File Name or File Content


github repo: https://github.com/IbrarYunus/Advanced_Programming.git

Unit Testing is done via batch files!

Note: Unit Tests are stricly limited to the state of the filesystem and hence any new file can cause assertions to fail.